山客見狀報警求助。<br />\n警員及消防到場，<br />\n在獅頭附近的空地上發現該幅巨幡，<br />\n警員一度搜尋有關人士惟未有發現，<br />\n列作發現橫額處理。<br />\n警方與消防在場商討後，<br />\n將巨幡割開分成5幅紮起，<br />\n帶走交相關部門跟進。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">據了解，該批人士在獅頭位置圖掛上巨幡時，因大風將巨幡吹反，未能成功掛上。</span><br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(source:<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180513/bkn-20180513104956302-0513_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180513%2Fbkn-20180513104956302-0513_00822_001.html&d=XeGbOuanAZPJpwXkrA1wSWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=7e02b171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180513/bkn-20180513104956302-0513_00822_001.html</a>)"},{"pid":"18795c047b8558acab31b17129e7066f41328645","tid":663093,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33de4ee16962bcdc66e30c2d3aa0132a93bbec1a","tid":663093,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:49:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63d4bf45d19096b291b1a3dfb70bad665e9fcfcf","tid":663093,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"98271228bdd2446fe847e13412f7acb2e9c6b67c","tid":663093,"uid":72457,"like":6,"dislike":84,"score":-78,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"又做埋D戇鳩野<br />\n只會比機會政府立法23條"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bBqzLdw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbBqzLdw.gif&h=c3496947&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"570f00bd35d5f16cf97ff29292a303e9fd2c3259","tid":663093,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589cfe5a1cc581ad84464d9f0113acde963ae32d","